            <div class="container">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-sm-12">

<p class=lead>With VANE tile API you can embed a lot of weather layers into your application. </p>
To get weather maps tiles or to apply your owm styles to predefined layers - launch the VANE <a href="http://home.owm.io/map_editor">Map Editor</a> tool under your OWM account.</br>
Please see a <a href="http://owm.io/docs/map_editor_2">detailed description</a> on how to use.<br/>

<div class="col-sm-8">


